<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-150] Create an appendix with all tunable options</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-150</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It would be &apos;nice to have&apos; a single source to list and possibly document every single tunable option in the Lustre code.  The Ops Manual should contain this list or table as an appendix.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This appendix could simply be an index to the section/page where the option is described in the Ops Manual.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
